pull_request.title: Describe goals in README
pull_request.body:
This is to get some discussion going on the goals of this project. 
I wrote a draft on where I was planning to go with this project, but I would like some input on that.
Please comment or suggest edits!

pull_request.title: Update MAINTAINERS.md
pull_request.body:
Forgot to set the maintainers when this was created from the template. This adds https://github.com/hanno-becker and myself. 

@cothan, do you also want to be included here? Suggest an edit please in case you want to maintain this repo.

review.body: The current list will be approved by the first TSC. As such I approve that we merge this update now. Any followups will be through that tsc meeting.

pull_request.title: Add Hanno Becker to TSC members
pull_request.body: I'd like to propose Hanno Becker from AWS as an additional TSC member. He is going to join me in maintaining https://github.com/pq-code-package/mlkem-c-aarch64.
